## Common Tasks

### Adding More QR Codes

1. Go to Dashboard
2. Click "Create QR Codes"
3. Fill in details
4. Download and use

### Viewing Registrations

1. Go to Dashboard
2. Click "View Registrations"
3. See all sign-ups in table format
4. Filter by date or QR code
5. Export to CSV/Excel

### Editing Your Form

1. Go to Dashboard
2. Click "Build Forms"
3. Select your form
4. Make changes
5. Save updates

### Checking Someone In

1. Go to Registrations
2. Find the person's name
3. Click "Check In"
4. Mark as checked in
5. Or scan their QR code

