## Getting Help

### In-App Tutorials

Look for the blue **?** button in the bottom-right corner of each page. Click it to start an interactive tutorial that walks you through that page's features.

### Tooltips

Hover over the small **?** icons next to labels for quick explanations.

### Empty States

When you haven't created something yet, you'll see helpful messages with "Create" buttons to get started.

---

## Tips for Success

### ğŸ“± Form Design
- **Keep it short:** 5-7 fields maximum
- **Use clear labels:** "Full Name" not just "Name"
- **Add examples:** Show format in placeholder text
- **Mark what's required:** Don't surprise users

### ğŸ¯ QR Code Placement
- **Make it visible:** Eye level, well-lit areas
- **Add instructions:** "Scan to Register"
- **Test it first:** Scan with your own phone
- **Multiple locations:** Use different QR codes to track which works best

### ğŸ“Š Data Management
- **Export regularly:** Back up your registration data
- **Check analytics:** See which QR codes perform best
- **Monitor in real-time:** Check dashboard during events
- **Follow up:** Export contact info for post-event communication

### âœ… Before Your Event
- [ ] Test QR code with multiple phones
- [ ] Print extra copies
- [ ] Share digital version via email/social
- [ ] Check registration form on mobile
- [ ] Set up check-in process
- [ ] Export existing registrations

---

## Troubleshooting

### QR Code Won't Scan
- âœ… Ensure good lighting
- âœ… Hold phone 6-12 inches away
- âœ… Make sure QR code is "Active" in dashboard
- âœ… Try a different phone/camera
- âœ… Check if QR code image is clear (not blurry)

### Didn't Receive Verification Email
- âœ… Check spam/junk folder
- âœ… Wait 5 minutes (can be delayed)
- âœ… Click "Resend Code"
- âœ… Verify email address is correct
- âœ… Add noreply@blessbox.com to contacts

### Registration Form Not Submitting
- âœ… Check required fields are filled
- âœ… Verify email format is correct
- âœ… Check internet connection
- âœ… Try refreshing the page
- âœ… Clear browser cache

### Can't See Registrations
- âœ… Ensure you're logged into correct account
- âœ… Check if organization is selected
- âœ… Refresh the page
- âœ… Verify registrations went to correct QR code set

