## Best Practices

### Security
- âœ… Use strong passwords
- âœ… Don't share login credentials
- âœ… Log out on shared computers
- âœ… Regularly export data backups

### Privacy
- âœ… Only collect necessary information
- âœ… Follow data protection laws (GDPR, CCPA)
- âœ… Secure sensitive data
- âœ… Delete old data when no longer needed

### Efficiency
- âœ… Create reusable form templates
- âœ… Use descriptive QR code names
- âœ… Set up check-in process in advance
- âœ… Export data regularly for analysis

